data.description: Gorgeous home in Wylie ISD with mountain views just outside city limits. Located in sought after neighborhood just minutes from town.  Open-concept features a Gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless GE appliances with double ovens and two pantry's. And a formal dining, a large breakfast room with built-in cabinetry and granite countertop for serving and a breakfast bar that can easily seat up to 8 persons. The luxurious Master bedroom suite is spacious with large walk-in shower, jetted tub and spacious walk-in closet . There are two additional bedrooms and a home office also located downstairs. Upstairs includes large second Living or Media room with additional space for movie snacks.  The 3rd car garage is equipped to serve as a shop with built-in shelving & electricity. Home office and Second Living features closets that could also serve as additional bedrooms. Home has spacious backyard for kids to play and a large covered patio with outdoor lighting and water misters.
